milestones.description: Roy Dias's 102 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for SL), surpassing Wettimuny's 86
Srikkanth's 95 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for IND), surpassing Vengsarkar's 88
Ranasinghe has conceded the most runs in an innings (78) in ODIs for SL, going past Mevan Pieris's record of 68
Vengsarkar and Srikkanth's 134-run partnership is IND's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 119 between Gaekwad and Amarnath
Sandeep Patil and Malhotra's 108-run partnership is IND's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 70 between Engineer and Ajit Wadekar
Roy Dias and Wettimuny's 170-run partnership is SL's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 139 between Roy Dias and Warnapura
Srikkanth has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (58) in an innings in ODIs for IND, going past Kapil Dev's 54
This is the highest match aggregate (558) involving teams India & Sri Lanka in ODIs
Vengsarkar has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (26) for IND, going past Gavaskar
Vengsarkar and Srikkanth's 134-run partnership is IND's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 123 between Gavaskar and Engineer
Roy Dias and Wettimuny's 170-run partnership is SL's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 139 between Warnapura and Roy Dias
